Method & normalisation

This report compares coded results across 2023 and 2025 using OrgCode as the unique join key and includes only organisations with IncludeIO = 1. Values were harmonised earlier into *_code (compact code) and *_short (human label). Where codes appear numeric, transitions are interpreted as direction of change. Missing values are shown as NA. Any unmatched raw values would be coded as UNK (should be rare after mapping).
